value.name: Hacking Universe
value.overview: Hacker Fedor has been trying all his life to find the parents who left him as a child. In this, he is helped by his faithful friends, Boris, a stylish coder, and Ignat, an introverted technician. Another attempt leads to the fact that hackers get involved in an intergalactic conflict between Earthlings and Komodians. Now the fate of the entire planet depends on Fedor, Boris and Ignat.
